{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make the sale of catapults/ammunition and carrying catapults in public illegal.",
        "additional_details": "Also ban companies selling catapults and ammunition in the UK, so they are not so easily accessible.\r\n \r\nI am an wildlife rescuer and believe we are currently in a wildlife crime pandemic. There has been an increase in reports of wildlife being attacked by groups of youths carrying catapults and ball bearings.\r\n75% of my call outs are due to apparent abuse of wildlife offences. \r\nWe think the law needs to change to give the Police more powers to arrest those carrying catapults.\r\n",
        "background": "Make it illegal to carry catapults in public places, so the police can arrest those carrying, especially in areas of known wildlife crime, regardless if ammunition is found or not.",
